|

<commentary>viditaivaṃvidhajñānasya jagad yathā tad darśayati—


yenetyādi | "sadasator utpādāyogād" ityādinājātaṃ jagad yena buddhaṃ pratyakṣato jñātaṃ tasya prtītyasamutpannā buddhiḥ śuddhaiva bodhato nirvedhataḥ | atas tasya dhīmato 'nābhogenābhogaṃ vinaiva nijaṃ sahajaṃ jagat satyam avitatham ||</commentary>

adhunā vikalpo 'pi nirvāṇam iti darśayati—avibhāvitetyādi | avibhāvitasambandho 'viditasambandho 'sau vikalpaḥ prītyasamutpannaḥ |